name: Scr4-Nokota
description:
One day, a robot sent on an expedition to an ancient city, captured a radio signal from the depths. Going in search of the source of the signal, he found an ancient database; connecting to it, he felt that someone's consciousness was being loaded into him. 
Thus, the mind of an old shaman who lived many years ago moved into the body of this robot. Having acquired the relics again, he began to restore his former strength.
